  "description": "# Open Outbox Relay: Performance & Reliability Overview\n\nThis dashboard provides a real-time view of the **Open Outbox Relay** health, throughput, and delivery efficiency. It is designed to monitor the lifecycle of events as they move from persistent storage (Transactional Outbox) to message brokers like Kafka, NATS, or Redis.\n\n### 🚀 Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)\n\n* **Throughput (EPS):** Measured in Events Per Second. Highlighting sustained delivery speeds across Success and Failure states.\n* **Batching Efficiency:** Tracks the effectiveness of `BATCH_SIZE` tuning, showing how many events are grouped per transaction.\n* **Delivery Health:** A visual ratio of successful deliveries vs. failed attempts, allowing for quick identification of downstream broker issues.\n* **Latency & Backoff:** Monitors the End-to-End time events spend in the outbox and ensures the relay respects backoff constraints during load.\n\n### 🛠 Prerequisites\n* **Collector:** OpenTelemetry (Go SDK) exported to Prometheus.\n* **Required Metrics:** `openoutbox_events_total`, `openoutbox_relay_state`, `openoutbox_events_e2e_latency_seconds_bucket`, etc.\n* **Template Variable:** This dashboard requires a `$DS_PROMETHEUS` data source variable.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "Monitors the lifecycle state of the Relay Engine. 1 = Active (Healthy), 2 = Paused (Publisher Down), 3 = Error (Critical/Storage Down).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "fixed"
          },
          "custom": {
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "hideFrom": {
              "legend": false,
              "tooltip": false,
              "viz": false
            },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineWidth": 0,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "decimals": 0,
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "1": {
                  "color": "green",
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "1: ACTIVE"
                },
                "2": {
                  "color": "yellow",
                  "index": 1,
                  "text": "2: PAUSED"
                },
                "3": {
                  "color": "red",
                  "index": 2,
                  "text": "3: ERROR"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "max": 3,
          "min": 0,
